This repository contains the syllabus, schedule, problem sets, pattern
reference, and project briefs for the course "Data Structures & Algorithms
in C++". You are welcome to read these materials, share links to this
repository, and use the problem lists for your own personal study.

You may not resell, repackage, or redistribute these materials as part of
another paid course or product, and you may not present them as your own
work, without written permission from the author.

The course lectures, recordings, and any private cohort materials are not
part of this repository and are licensed only to enrolled students.
